0Yadav's%20ornaments%2C%20put%20his%20body%20in%20the%20SUV%20and%20set%20it%20on%20fire.%C2%A0The%20charred%20SUV%20was%20found%20in%20a%20forest%20area%20in%20Dadri%20on%20Monday%20night.%20A%20body%20inside%20the%20car%20was%20identified%20as%20Sanjay%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20family%20members%20had%20told%20them%20that%20Yadav%20went%20to%20meet%20his%20friends%20Vishal%20Rajput%20and%20Jeet%20Choudhary%20and%20alleged%20that%20they%20must%20have%20murdered%20him.%20Accordingly%2C%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20and%20the%20accused%20were%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20questioning%2C%20Vishal%20and%20Jeet%20admitted%20to%20murdering%20Yadav%20to%20loot%20money%20and%20jewellery%2C%20police%20said.%20They%20said%20the%20realtor%20visited%20them%20Monday%20evening%20and%20three%20had%20beer.%20Later%2C%20Vishal%20and%20Jeet%20allegedly%20choked%20Yadav%20with%20a%20dog%20collar%20and%20looted%20his%20ornaments.%20The%20accused%20then%20put%20Yadav's%20body%20in%20the%20rear%20seat%20of%20the%20SUV%20and%20used%20petrol%20to%20set%20the%20vehicle%20on%20fire.%20Jeet%20suffered%20minor%20burns%20while%20setting%20the%20SUV%20afire%2C%20police%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20recovered%20cash%2C%20two%20gold%20rings%2C%20a%20bracelet%20and%20a%20gold%20chain%20from%20the%20accused.%20They%20have%20also%20found%20the%20dog%20collar%20used%20in%20the%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVishal%20Rajput%20and%20Jeet%20Choudhary%20got%20him%20(Yadav)%20drunk.%20They%20choked%20him%20with%20a%20dog%20collar.%20To%20dispose%20of%20the%20body%2C%20they%20drove%20to%20a%20deserted%20area.%20They%20then%20set%20the%20SUV%20on%20fire%20with%20the%20body%20inside%20it.%20The%20accused%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20jail%20and%20further%20probe%20is%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ashok%20Kumar%2C%20Additional%20DCP%2C%20Greater%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729743480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F