0millionaire%20and%20pioneer%20in%20anti-ageing%20research%2C%20recently%20shared%20his%20astonishing%20transformation%20on%20social%20media%2C%20revealing%20how%20he%20reversed%20male%20pattern%20baldness%20and%20restored%20his%20hair's%20natural%20colour%20in%20under%20a%20year.%20Through%20a%20thread%20on%20X%2C%20Mr%20Johnson%20unveiled%20his%20comprehensive%20regimen%20for%20preventing%20hair%20loss%20and%20maintaining%20lush%2C%20healthy%20locks.%20Despite%20being%20expected%20to%20be%20bald%20by%20now%2C%20he%20credited%20nutritional%2C%20topical%2C%20and%20light%20treatments%20for%20his%20remarkable%20transformation.%20The%20millionaire%20also%20encouraged%20men%20to%20act%20early%20and%20take%20proactive%20steps%20to%20preserve%20their%20hair%2C%20insisting%20it's%20possible%20to%20maintain%20a%20full%20head%20of%20hair%20%26quot%3Bwell%20into%20your%2040s%20and%20beyond.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Genetically%2C%20I%20should%20be%20bald.%20I%20started%20to%20lose%20my%20hair%20and%20go%20gray%20in%20my%20late%2020s.%20Now%2C%20at%2047%2C%20I've%20got%20a%20full%20head%20of%20hair%20and%20~70%25%20of%20my%20gray%20is%20gone.%20Here%20how%20I%20did%20it%2C''%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGenetically%2C%20I%20should%20be%20bald.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20started%20to%20lose%20my%20hair%20and%20go%20gray%20in%20my%20late%2020s.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%2C%20at%2047%2C%20I've%20got%20a%20full%20head%20of%20hair%20and%20~70%25%20of%20my%20gray%20is%20gone.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHere%20how%20I%20did%20it..%20%F0%9F%A7%B5%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVLuCVwTeMM%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVLuCVwTeMM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bryan%20Johnson%20%2Fdd%20(%40bryan_johnson)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.c