uring%20which%20the%20PCB%20chairman%2C%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%2C%20was%20also%20present.%20Sources%20told%20Geo%20News%20that%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20PCB%20officials%20assured%20the%20ICC%20board%20members%20that%20the%20upgradation%20of%20the%20three%20stadiums%20that%20will%20host%20the%20matches%20of%20the%20marquee%20event%20will%20be%20completed%20within%20the%20stipulated%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaqvi%20has%20also%20invited%20ICC%20board%20members%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20review%20the%20preparations%20made%20for%20the%20tournament.%20The%20Champions%20Trophy%20will%20begin%20next%20year%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20there%20are%20certain%20challenges%20that%20need%20to%20be%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUncertainty%20continues%20to%20loom%20over%20India%20going%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20mega%20event.%20Since%202008's%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20India%20has%20not%20played%20any%20cricket%20tournaments%20in%20Pakistan%20due%20to%20tense%20relationships%20between%20both%20nations%20because%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20series%20played%20from%20December%202012%20to%20January%202013%20in%20India%20marked%20the%20final%20bilateral%20series%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20Since%20then%2C%20both%20nations%20have%20only%20clashed%20at%20ICC%20tournaments%20and%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Pakistan%20travelled%20to%20India%20on%20three%20occasions%20since%20the%202008%20Asia%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20reports%20started%20to%20surface%20about%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20looking%20at%20three%20options%20regarding%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20ICC%20is%20either%20looking%20to%20have%20the%20tournament%20go%20ahead%20in%20Pakistan%20as%20planned%20or%20take%20place%20in%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20hybrid%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20this%20hybrid%20model%2C%20matches%20for%20India%20and%20knockout%20stage%20games%20will%20take%20place%20in%20Dubai.%20The%20third%20option%20is%20the%20entire%20tournament%2C%20taking%20place%20outside%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20Dubai%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20or%20South%20Africa%20as%20possible%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20have%20not%20hosted%20any%20major%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20event%20since%20the%201996%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20it%20co-hosted%20with%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729735740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F4753f54_india-pakistan-afp_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Famid-champions-trophy-deadlock-icc-delivers-big-boost-to-pakistan-cricket-board-6845725%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recently%2C%20reports%20started%20to%20surface%20about%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20looking%20at%20three%20options%20regarding%20hosting%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Famid-champions-trophy-deadlock-icc-delivers-big-boost-to-pakistan-cricket-board-6845725%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moment%20passenger%20steers%20bus%20to%20safety%20after%20driver's%20collapse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729735740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2e6a%2Flive%2Fa0142f80-91aa-11ef-b3c2-754b6219680e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc4gvq4qyj24o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20driver%20suffered%20a%20medical%20emergency%20and%20fell%20out%20of%20his%20seat%2C%20transport%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22a