first%20few%20minutes%20of%20the%20movie%2C%20where%20we%20see%20him%20kill%20a%20drug%20dealer's%20lackey%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20relieve%20himself%20of%20the%20curse%20by%20passing%20it%20on%20to%20another%20person%20(the%20first%20film%20established%20that%20the%20only%20loophole%20for%20escaping%20the%20Smile%20Entity%20involves%20killing%20another%20person%20yourself%20and%20making%20sure%20someone%20sees%20it).%20Things%20go%20sideways%20almost%20immediately%2C%20when%20Joel%20accidentally%20shoots%20and%20kills%20the%20drug%20dealer%20himself%2C%20then%20is%20run%20down%20and%20killed%20by%20a%20car%20when%20he%20flees%20the%20drug%20dealer's%20gang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20character%2C%20low-level%20drug%20dealer%20Lewis%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flukas-gage-shares-video-twitter-director-unmuted-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELukas%20Gage%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20is%20the%20unwitting%20recipient%20of%20the%20curse%20after%20he%20accidentally%20sees%20Joel%20kill%20both%20the%20dealer%20and%20his%20lackey%20when%20he's%20stopping%20by%20to%20pick%20up%20drugs.%20But%20Lewis%2C%20too%2C%20isn't%20long%20for%20this%20world%3B%20he's%20only%20the%20vehicle%20by%20which%20the%20entity's%20curse%20is%20passed%20on%20to%20our%20new%20leading%20lady%20%E2%80%94%20troubled%20pop%20star%20Skye%20Riley%20(Naomi%20Scott).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222601%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naomi%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BSmile%202%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67181b6e9b3250dbbce94e1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221951%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENaomi%20Scott%20as%20Skye%20Riley%20in%20%26quot%3BSmile%202.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EParamount%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20meet%20her%2C%20Skye%20is%20a%20recovering%20drug%20addict.%20After%20a%20car%20crash%20left%20her%20badly%20injured%20and%20killed%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20actor%20Paul%20Hudson%20(played%20by%20Ray%20Nicholson%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Jack%20Nicholson)%2C%20who%20was%20driving%2C%20she's%20preparing%20for%20her%20comeback%20world%20tour.%20Still%20in%20chronic%20pain%20but%20unable%20to%20get%20a%20doctor%20to%20prescribe%20her%20painkillers%20due%20to%20her%20past%20substance%20misuse%2C%20Skye%20turns%20to%20her%20former%20high%20school%20classmate%20Lewis%20to%20get%20Vicodin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELewis%20is%20on%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20the%20Smile%20Entity's%20curse%20when%20Skye%20arrives%20at%20his%20apartment.%20Strung%20out%20on%20coke%20and%20wildly%20paranoid%20after%20days%20of%20seeing%20the%20smiling%20creature%2C%20Lewis%20suddenly%20(and%20graphically)%20starts%20grinning%20at%20Skye%20before%20calmly%20smashing%20his%20own%20face%20open%20with%20a%20gym%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20we%20don't%20see%20the%20entity%20onscreen%2C%20viewers%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20first%20movie%20recognize%20that%20Lewis%20was%20possessed%2C%20and%20has%20now%20passed%20the%20curse%20onto%20Skye.%20Now%2C%20Skye%20must%20deal%20with%20a%20literal%20demon%20on%20top%20of%20her%20metaphorical%20personal%20demons%3A%20specifically%2C%20the%20mental%20health%20problems%20that%20have%20led%20her%20to%20push%20away%20everyone%20close%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20includes%20her%20mom-manager%20Elizabeth%20(Rosemarie%20DeWitt)%2C%20her%20sweet%20and%20well-intentioned%20assistant%20Joshua%20(Miles%20Gutierrez-Riley)%2C%20and%20her%20ex-best%20friend%20Gemma%20(Dylan%20Gelula)%2C%20who%20cut%20ties%20with%20Skye%20right%20before%20her%20near-fatal%20accident%20the%20year%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295a0603c-ed18-4b3a-8631-56e6d8efe65f%5C%22%3EThe%20'Smile%202'%20ending%20features%20twists%20upon%20twists%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222773%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Naomi%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BSmile%202%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6718214f01ea6d83dee34da1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENaomi%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BSmile%202.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EParamount%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20film%2C%20Skye%20contends%20with%20being%20haunted%20by%20the%20entity%2C%20which%20often%20takes%20the%20form%20of%20her%20overzealous%20fans%20(including%20one%20creeper%20from%20a%20meet-and-greet%20who%20attacked%20her).%20She%20gets%20support%20from%20her%20former%20friend%20Gemma%2C%20who%20surprisingly%20easily%20agrees%20to%20forgive%20Skye%20for%20her%20toxic%20behavior%20throughout%20their%20friendship%20when%20Skye%20reaches%20out%20for%20help%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20curse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Skye%20is%20also%20receiving%20incessant%20text%20messages%20from%20a%20stranger%20who%20tells%20her%20that%20they%20know%20she%20was%20at%20Lewis'%20apartment%20the%20night%20he%20died.%20After%20a%20disastrous%20charity%20appearance%20leads%20to%20a%20meltdown%20when%20the%20entity%20takes%20the%20form%20of%20Skye's%20dead%20boyfriend%2C%20she%20finally%20agrees%20to%20meet%20with%20the%20texter%20and%20learns%20he's%20a%20potential%20ally%3A%20Morris%20(Peter%20Jacobson)%2C%20an%20ER%20nurse%2C%20who%20tells%20her%20that%20his%20brother%20was%20also%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20Smile%20Entity%20further%20back%20in%20the%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20meeting%2C%20Morris%20tells%20Skye%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20only%20way%20they%20can%20stop%20the%20entity%20for%20good%20is%20to%20stop%20Skye's%20heart%20while%20she's%20alone%20in%20a%20room%2C%20temporarily%20killing%20her%20and%20thereby%20depriving%20the%20entity%20of%20a%20host%20to%20jump%20over%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Skye%20is%20horrified%20by%20the%20suggestion.%20But%20things%20rapidly%20get%20even%20worse%20for%20her.%20Later%2C%20she%20returns%20to%20her%20apartment%2C%20where%20she's%20confronted%20by%20the%20entity%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20the%20form%20of%20a%20swarm%20of%20her%20fans.%20They%20attack%20her%2C%20and%20one%20reaches%20its%20hand%20into%20her%20mouth%2C%20apparently%20to%20possess%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Skye%20awakens%2C%20she's%20in%20a%20private%20rehab%20facility%2C%20being%20watched%20over%20by%20her%20mother%20and%20Joshua.%20Left%20alone%2C%20Skye%20and%20her%20mother%20have%20a%20confrontation%20where%20her%20mother%20rails%20against%20her%20for%20letting%20everyone%20down%20by%20asking%20to%20cancel%20the%20tour.%20Soon%2C%20Skye's%20mother%20is%20revealed%20to%20be%20the%20entity%20in%20disguise%2C%20which%20we%20see%20stab%20itself%20repeatedly%20with%20a%20broken%20shard%20of%20mirror.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkye%20goes%20to%20flee%20before%20realizing%20she's%20covered%20in%20blood%3A%20It%20looks%20like%20she%20killed%20her%20own%20mother%2C%20despite%20Skye%20(and%20the%20audience)%20seeing%20the%20entity%20stab%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222773%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rosemarie%20DeWitt%20and%20Naomi%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BSmile%202%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671821ce01ea6d83dee34da8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERosemarie%20DeWitt%20and%20Naomi%20Scott%20in%20%26quot%3BSmile%202.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EParamount%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20panic%2C%20Skye%20flees%20the%20hospital%20after%20a%20confrontation%20with%20Joshua%2C%20some%20doctors%2C%20and%20rehab%20security.%20She%20runs%20into%20Gemma%2C%20who%20was%20en%20route%20to%20the%20rehab%20facility%20to%20visit%20her%2C%20and%20steals%20an%20Uber%20driver's%20car%20at%20gunpoint%20to%20head%20to%20Staten%20Island%3B%20having%20run%20out%20of%20options%20and%20not%20wanting%20anyone%20else%20to%20die%2C%20she's%20agreed%20to%20meet%20Morris%20to%20enact%20his%20plan%20to%20stop%20her%20heart%20to%20defeat%20the%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGemma%20hops%20in%20the%20car%20with%20Skye%2C%20insisting%20on%20sticking%20with%20her%20and%20saying%20she's%20her%20%26quot%3Bride%20or%20die.%26quot%3B%20The%20heartwarming%20moment%20is%20cut%20short%20when%20the%20%3Cem%3Ereal%3C%2Fem%3E%20Gemma%20calls%20Skye%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20revealing%20that%20the%20entity%20has%20been%20Gemma%20all%20along%3A%20Gemma%20never%20actually%20called%20Skye%20back%20or%20came%20to%20see%20her%20after%20Skye's%20initial%20voicemail%20apologizing%20for%20their%20falling%20out%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entity%20vanishes%20after%20taunting%20Skye%20by%20telling%20her%20that%20Gemma%20hates%20her%2C%20revealing%20that%20Skye%2C%20not%20Gemma%2C%20has%20been%20driving%20the%20car%20the%20whole%20time.%20Skye%20arrives%20at%20the%20abandoned%20Pizza%20Hut%20that%20Morris%20has%20rented%20out%20%E2%80%94%20its%20freezer%2C%20he%20says%2C%20will%20allow%20them%20to%20get%20her%20body%20temperature%20low%20enough%20to%20prevent%20brain%20damage%20while%20they%20stop%20her%20heart%20for%20nine%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorris%20sets%20everything%20up%20in%20the%20freezer%2C%20which%20conveniently%20has%20a%20door%20that%20will%20only%20open%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20then%20leaves%20to%20go%20%26quot%3Bget%20something.%26quot%3B%20At%20that%20point%2C%20Skye%20sees%20the%20version%20of%20herself%20critically%20injured%20after%20the%20car%20crash%20suspended%20from%20the%20ceiling%3A%20It's%20the%20Smile%20Entity%2C%20having%20taken%20the%20form%20of%20her%20past%20self.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entity-as-past-Skye%20taunts%20Skye%2C%20telling%20her%2C%20%26quot%3BYou'll%20never%20escape%20who%20you%20truly%20are%20on%20the%20inside.%26quot%3B%20Skye%20fights%20off%20the%20creature%20and%20manages%20to%20get%20her%20hands%20on%20the%20injection%20to%20stop%20her%20own%20heart.%20This%20appears%20to%20work%2C%20as%20the%20entity%20shrieks%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20reveal%20it's%20yet%20another%20fakeout%20and%20none%20of%20this%20batt