%20while%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20outs%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20remaining%20members%20of%20the%20Family%20post-divorce%2C%20she%20was%20informed%20of%20%26quot%3Bshady%26quot%3B%20business%20dealings%20involving%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20reviewed%20her%20balance%20at%20the%20bank%2C%20she%20was%20astounded%20to%20see%20that%20her%20checking%20account%20was%20drastically%20lower%20than%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20couldn't%20be%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenz%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20been%20making%20around%20a%20million%20dollars%20a%20year%20for%20several%20seasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20government%20taxes%2C%20paying%20her%20team%2C%20yearly%20expenses%2C%20and%20%24200%2C000%20going%20toward%20the%20restaurant%2C%20Lenz%20estimated%20that%20she%20should%20have%20had%20%242.4%20million%20in%20her%20account.%20Instead%2C%20there%20was%20%24220%2C000%20remaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20%24200%2C000%20was%20more%20than%20many%20people%20would%20see%20in%20their%20whole%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Lenz%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'd%20spent%2020%20years%20building%20a%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20she%20was%20filled%20with%20feelings%20of%20self-loathing%20after%20building%20up%20her%20acting%20career%2C%20only%20for%20her%20earnings%20to%20then%20be%20depleted%20by%20the%20cult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20horrifying%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fbethany-joy-lenz-lost-millions-to-a-cult-exclusive-8728595%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20knowing%20how%20I%20was%20going%20to%20make%20rent%20because%20all%20the%20money%20was%20gone%2C%20it%20was%20legitimately%20incredibly%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Lenz%20said%20that%20the%20cult%20controlled%20her%20career%20and%20Les%20deterred%20her%20from%20acc