48%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20Perplexity%20is%20scraping%20copyrighted%20work%20to%20feed%20its%20search%20engine%20and%2C%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20is%20routing%20would-be%20readers%20and%20customers%20away%20from%20their%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody's%20coming%20to%20Perplexity%20to%20ingest%20their%20news.%20People%20are%20directly%20going%20to%20%5BThe%5D%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%26quot%3B%20Srinivas%20said.%20He%20explained%20Perplexity's%20goal%20as%20helping%20users%20%3Cem%3Edigest%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20news.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20come%20to%20Perplexity%20for%20understanding%20the%20news%20in%20the%20context%20of%20what%20they%20already%20know.%20'How%20does%20this%20news%20affect%20me%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20interested%20in%20taking%20the%20exact%20content%20and%20resurfacing%20it.%20We%20are%20not%20trying%20to%20be%20the%20news%20alternative%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20later%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20try%20our%20best%20to%20engage%20and%20communicate%20what%20the%20goals%20of%20our%20product%20are%20and%20how%20they%20can%20be%20symbiotic%20with%20the%20existing%20news%20outlets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20company%20has%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Fnyt-sends-ai-startup-perplexity-cease-desist-notice-over-content-use-wsj-reports-2024-10-15%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0it%20does%20not%20scrape%20data%20for%20training%20large%20language%20models%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20scours%20the%20internet%2C%20creating%20an%20index%20of%20web%20pages%20for%20its%20models%20to%20reference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entrepreneur%20stayed%20coolheaded%20as%20WSJ%20reporter%20Deepa%20Seetharaman%20lobbed%20questions%20about%20Perplexity's%20cash%20flow%20and%20claims%20by%20news%20outlets%20that%20it%20doesn't%20make%20citations%20clear.%20Srinivas%20acknowledged%20the%20tech%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20perfect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20working%20with%20a%20piece%20of%20technology%20that%20is%20constantly%20improving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20responded%20to%20a%20question%20about%20plagiarism.%20%26quot%3BEven%20yesterday%2C%20Anthropic%20released%20another%20version%20of%20their%20models%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-computer-use-ai-explainer-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClaude%203.5%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20getting%20better%20and%20better%20every%20few%20months.%20So%20whatever%20issues%20exist%20today%20are%20a%20new%20set%20of%20issues%20that%20did%20not%20exist%20one%20or%20two%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20interview%2C%20Srinivas%20defended%20the%20company's%20modus%20operandi%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20Journal's%20publisher%20in%20June%20about%20potentially%20striking%20up%20a%20contract%20that%20would%20allow%20Perplexity%20to%20share%20future%20ad%20revenues%20with%20the%20publisher.%20He%20didn't%20specify%20the%20contract's%20contents%20but%20said%20the%20conversation%20went%20dark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20certainly%20were%20very%20surprised%20about%20the%20lawsuit%20because%20we%20actually%20wanted%20a%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20Srinivas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20the%20company%20will%20start%20selling%20ads%20against%20popular%20searches%2C%20Srinivas%20said.%20So%2C%20for%20example%2C%20a%20user%20can%20ask%20Perplexity%20about%20a%20shoe%20company%20that%20has%20just%20gone%20public%20on%20Wall%20Street.%20The%20search%20engine%20will%20return%20a%20summary%20of%20the%20shoemaker's%20stock%20debut%20with%20sources%20and%20citations.%20If%20a%20shoe%20brand%20pays%20to%20advertise%20in%20the%20results%2C%20Perplexity%20will%20share%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20money%20it%20makes%20with%20publishers%20whose%20content%20it%20used%20to%20answer%20the%20query.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20only%20exist%20if%20we%20make%20money%20of%20our%20own%2C%20too%2C%20not%20just%20keep%20fundraising%2C%26quot%3B%20Srinivas%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20when%20we%20start%20making%20money%20of%20our%20own%2C%20that%20will%20certainly%20benefit%20all%20the%20publishers%20and%20ensure%20they%20also%20continue%20to%20flourish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20last%20week%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20sent%20Perplexity%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyt-sues-open-ai-microsoft-alleging-trained-chatgpt-off-content-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecease-and-desist%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeking%20to%20end%20the%20practice%20of%20using%20its%20stories%20to%20train%20chatbots.%20The%20news%20outlet%20is%20also%20suing%20OpenAI%20and%20Microsoft%20for%20copyright%20infringement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20hopes%20to%20turn%20profitable%20in%20the%20span%20of%20three%20to%20five%20years%20from%20selling%20subscriptions%20and%20advertisements%2C%20according%20to%20Srinivas.%20He%20acknowledged%20that%20while%20Perplexity%20isn't%20training%20large%20language%20models%20and%20doesn't%20need%20to%20raise%20as%20much%20capital%20as%20an%20OpenAI%20or%20Anthropic%2C%20the%20influx%20of%20investor%20cash%20allows%20it%20to%20move%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFundraising%20obviously%20helps%20us%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20the%20product%20and%20keep%20improving%20the%20product%20but%20not%20be%20overly%20worried%20about%20the%20financials%2C%26quot%3B%20Srinivas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-ceo-lawsuits-tensions-dow-jones-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729716911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6719583901ea6d83dee39d1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg