resh%20beef%20patties%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20being%20examined%20as%20potential%20sources%20of%20contamination.%20The%20company%20said%20that%20all%20potentially%20affected%20food%20products%20have%20been%20recalled%20from%20its%20impacted%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20executives%20said%20initial%20indicators%20point%20to%20the%20slivered%20onions%20as%20the%20more%20likely%20source%2C%20though%20they're%20not%20ruling%20out%20the%20fresh%20beef%20patties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20said%20that%20while%20slivered%20onions%20are%20used%20on%20a%20breakfast%20sandwich%20in%20some%20markets%2C%20that%20menu%20item%20isn't%20impacted%20as%20it%20was%20not%20available%20in%20the%20affected%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20this%20case%20compares%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-hasnt-overcome-e-coli-fears-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprior%20E.%20coli%20outbreaks%20linked%20to%20Chipotle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20McDonald's%20representatives%20said%20the%20two%20appear%20to%20be%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chipotle%20cases%20involved%20the%20handling%20and%20preparation%20of%20food%20in%20restaurants%2C%20McDonald's%20executives%20said.%20This%20outbreak%20involves%20potentially%20contaminated%20ingredients%20arriving%20from%20a%20supplier.%20The%20McDonald's%20cases%20also%20represent%20a%20relatively%20low%20percentage%20of%20its%20overall%20food%20served%20and%20in%20an%20isolated%20geographic%20area%2C%20and%20contamination%20hasn't%20affected%20other%20menu%20items%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChipotle%20agreed%20to%20pay%20a%20%2425%20million%20fine%20in%202020%20to%20resolve%20criminal%20charges%20related%20to%20foodborne%20illnesses%20that%20caused%20over%201%2C100%20people%20to%20get%20sick%20between%202015%20and%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fmcdonalds-restore-confidence-e-coli-outbreak-linked-quarter-pounders-p-rcna176742%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20McDonald's%20USA%20president%20Joe%20Erlinger%20said%20the%20company%20is%20working%20closely%20with%20federal%20agencies%20to%20identify%20and%20contain%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20has%20been%20contaminated%20product%20within%20our%20supply%20chain%2C%20it's%20very%20likely%20worked%20itself%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BCertainly%20we'll%20be%20working%20with%20the%20CDC%20and%20cooperating%20with%20them%20on%20the%20investigation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20E.%20coli%20contaminations%20can%20be%20associated%20with%20raw%20or%20undercooked%20meat%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20the%20briefing%20that%20the%20beef%20used%20in%20its%20Quarter%20Pounder%20hamburgers%20is%20sourced%20from%20multiple%20different%20suppliers%20in%20the%20affected%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20officials%20said%20that%20multiple%20restaurants%20would%20have%20had%20to%20fail%20to%20prepare%20the%20meals%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fsites%2Fcorp%2Fnfl%2Fpdf%2FMcDonald%2527s%2520Food%2520Safety%2520Fact%2520Sheet.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estandards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20specify%20burgers%20must%20be%20cooked%20to%20an%20internal%20temperature%20of%20175%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20%E2%80%94%2015%20degrees%20higher%20than%20the%20threshold%20where%20E.%20coli%20is%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20said%20it%20performs%20periodic%20quality%20control%20checks%20throughout%20each%20day%20of%20operation%20and%20that%20the%20cases%20identified%20by%20the%20CDC%20spanned%20a%20nearly%20two-week%20period.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20roughly%20a%20million%20quarter%20pounders%20are%20usually%20sold%20in%20that%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20said