%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERenowned%20filmmaker%20Payal%20Kapadia%20discusses%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20independent%20cinema%20in%20India%20and%20the%20need%20for%20structural%20reforms.%20Her%20film%2C%20All%20We%20Imagine%20As%20Light%2C%20premieres%20on%20November%2022%20after%20winning%20the%20Grand%20Prix%20at%20Cannes.%20Kapadia%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20grants%20and%20support%20systems%20for%20indie%20filmmakers%20to%20enhance%20distribution%20opportunities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpayal-kapadia-echoes-anurag-kashyaps-concerns-over-lack-of-support-for-indie-films-structural-changes-needed%2Farticleshow%2F114518544.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Public%20Spat%2C%20Legal%20Battle%20Between%20Jagan%20Reddy%2C%20Sister%20Over%20Property%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20feud%20over%20property%20between%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20and%20his%20sister%20YS%20Sharmila%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20high-profile%20legal%20battle.%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20written%20to%20the%20National%20Company%20Law%20Tribunal%20or%20NCLT%2C%20seeking%20to%20nullify%20her%20%26quot%3Billegal'%20transfer%20of%20shares%20in%20Saraswati%20Power%20and%20Industries%20Private%20Limited%20to%20herself%20and%20their%20mother%20YS%20Vijayalakshmi.%20He%20also%20wrote%20to%20her%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20deceit%20and%20declaring%20that%20he%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20honouring%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20they%20had%20entered.%20After%20the%20contents%20of%20his%20letter%20became%20known%2C%20her%20written%20response%20to%20him%20has%20also%20gone%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20said%20there%20was%20no%20more%20affection%20between%20the%20two%2C%20Sharmila%20has%20accused%20him%20of%20not%20distributing%20assets%20equally%20between%20the%20four%20grandchildren%20of%20YS%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy%2C%20as%20desired%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2010%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20and%20his%20wife%20Bharathi%20Reddy%20had%20petitioned%20NCLT%2C%20asking%20the%20company%20to%20reinstate%20them%20as%20shareholders%20with%20the%20same%20equity%20shares%20as%20before%20the%20transfers%20were%20made%20by%20Sharmila.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20public%20falling%20out%20with%20her%20brother%2C%20YS%20Sharmila%20had%20floated%20her%20own%20party%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSR%20Telangana%20party%2C%20however%2C%20was%20merged%20with%20the%20Congress%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20elections.%20YS%20Sharmila%20was%20made%20the%20chief%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Congress%2C%20and%20she%20has%20sharply%20attacked%20Mr%20Reddy%2C%20who%20was%20Chief%20Minister%20at%20the%20time.%20She%20had%20also%20contested%20and%20lost%20from%20the%20Kadapa%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20against%20her%20cousin%20Avinash%20during%20the%20elections%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20petition%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20and%20his%20wife%20alleged%20that%20share%20transfers%20to%20Sharmila%20and%20Vijayamma%20were%20carried%20out%20through%20a%20Board%20resolution%20in%20July%202024%20without%20following%20proper%20legal%20procedure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20also%20said%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20entered%20into%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20with%20Sharmila%20in%20August%202019%20to%20transfer%20certain%20properties%20and%20shares%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20love%20and%20affection%26quot%3B%20but%20this%20transfer%20was%20never%20executed.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20rivalry%20between%20the%20siblings%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20changed%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20share%20transfers%20were%20made%20in%20violation%20of%20this%20MoU%20and%20were%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeceitful%20deviance%20of%20law%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Reddy%20argued%20that%20the%20transfer%20of%20shares%20was%20%26quot%3Binvalid%2C%20illegal%2C%20void%2C%20and%20unlawful%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCLT%20has%20issued%20notices%20to%20all%20respondents%20and%20scheduled%20the%20next%20hearing%20for%20November%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20had%20also%20written%20to%20his%20sister%20on%20August%2027%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20along%20with%20the%20ancestral%20property%20inherited%20from%20their%20father%20YS%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%2C%20he%20had%20also%20built%20his%20own%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOut%20of%20the%20sheer%20love%20and%20affection%2C%20I%20always%20bore%20towards%20you%20as%20my%20sister%2C%20I%20had%20also%20expressed%20my%20intention%20that%2C%20unrelated%20to%20any%20consideration%20and%20purely%20out%20of%20love%20and%20affection%2C%20I%20intended%20to%20effect%20transfer%20of%20certain%20properties%20to%20you%20at%20a%20future%20point%20of%20time.%20This%20was%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20amount%20of%20approximately%20Rs.200%20crores%20already%20given%20to%20you%20directly%20or%20through%20our%20mother%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20or%20so.%20This%20too%20was%20given%20by%20me%20out%20of%20my%20sheer%20love%20and%20affection%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20his%20affection%2C%20Sharmila%20made%20several%20false%20statements%20publicly%20which%20caused%20personal%20disrepute%2C%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20this%20and%20other%20actions%20undertaken%20by%20you%2C%20it%20makes%20me%20wonder%20why%20there%20should%20be%20any%20love%20and%20affection%20or%20fondness%20towards%20you%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20letter%20on%20September%2012%2C%20Sharmila%20wrote%20that%20Mr%20Reddy%20was%20not%20acting%20in%20accordance%20of%20the%20will%20of%20their%20late%20father%20to%20distribute%20the%20property%20equally%20among%20all%20four%20of%20his%20grandchildren.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20father%20was%20unequivocal%20in%20his%20instructions%20that%20all%20four%20of%20his%20grandchildren%20are%20to%20share%20equally%20in%20all%20assets%20that%20existed%20during%20his%20lifetime%2C%20whether%20they%20pertain%20to%20Bharathi%20Cements%2C%20Sakshi%2C%20or%20any%20other%20ventures%20initiated%20prior%20to%20his%20passing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContending%20that%20the%20transfer%20of%20shares%20was%20part%20of%20the%20property%20sharing%20%26quot%3Bsettlement%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%20you%20had%20the%20upper%20hand%2C%20you%20did%20bulldoze%20your%20way%20and%20we%20agreed%20to%20a%20settlement%20as%20stated%20in%20the%20MOU.%20Since%20you%20are%20my%20elder%20brother%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20resolving%20family%20disputes%2C%20I%20agreed%20to%20give%20up%20my%20equal%20share.%20Thus%2C%20under%20the%20MoU%20executed%20on%2031.08.2019%2C%20only%20a%20few%20properties%20were%20assigned%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20now%20chosen%20to%20file%20cases%20against%20your%20own%20mother%20and%20deprive%20your%20own%20sister%20and%20her%20children%20of%20properties%20to%20which%20they%20are%20entitled%20under%20the%20MoU.%20I%20am%20appalled%20at%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20you%20have%20strayed%20from%20the%20path%20of%20our%20noble%20father%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20criticised%20Mr%20Reddy's%20intervention%20in%20her%20political%20career%2C%20claiming%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20of%20him%20to%20suggest%20that%20she%20sign%20a%20clause%20that%20binds%20her%20from%20speaking%20against%20him%20or%20their%20cousin%20Avinash%20from%20public%20platforms.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729709100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F7mhanj8k_jagan-reddy-650_625x300_31_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpublic-spat