esofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faamir-khan-and-suriya-to-shoot-for-ghajini-2-in-hindi-and-tamil-simultaneously-allu-aravind-to-produce-ghajini-sequel%2Farticleshow%2F114516951.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBRICS%20Is%20For%20The%20Fairies%20Until%20China%2C%20India%20Get%20Serious%2C%26quot%3B%20Says%20Mr%20'BRICS'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20the%20BRICS%20group%20ever%20challenging%20the%20US%20dollar%20is%20for%20the%20fairies%20as%20long%20as%20China%20and%20India%20remain%20so%20divided%20and%20refuse%20to%20cooperate%20on%20trade%2C%20the%20former%20Goldman%20Sachs%20economist%20who%20came%20up%20with%20the%20BRIC%20acronym%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20is%20using%20the%20summit%20of%20BRICS%20leaders%20to%20show%20that%20Western%20attempts%20to%20isolate%20Russia%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20have%20failed%20and%20that%20Russia%20is%20building%20ties%20with%20the%20rising%20powers%20of%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen-Goldman%20Sachs%20chief%20economist%20Jim%20O'Neill%20introduced%20the%20term%20BRIC%20in%202001%20in%20a%20research%20paper%20that%20underlined%20the%20massive%20growth%20potential%20of%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%20and%20China%20-%20and%20the%20need%20to%20reform%20global%20governance%20to%20include%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20the%20BRICS%20can%20be%20some%20genuine%20global%20economic%20club%2C%20it's%20obviously%20a%20bit%20out%20there%20with%20the%20fairies%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20the%20G7%20can%20be%2C%20and%20it's%20very%20disturbing%20that%20they%20see%20themselves%20as%20some%20kind%20of%20alternative%20global%20thing%2C%20because%20it's%20obviously%20not%20feasible%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Neill%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20to%20me%20basically%20to%20be%20a%20symbolic%20annual%20gathering%20where%20important%20emerging%20countries%2C%20particularly%20noisy%20ones%20like%20Russia%2C%20but%20also%20China%2C%20can%20basically%20get%20together%20and%20highlight%20how%20good%20it%20is%20to%20be%20part%20of%20something%20that%20doesn't%20involve%20the%20US%20and%20that%20global%20governance%20isn't%20good%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Neill%2C%20who%20admitted%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bhave%20Mr%20BRICS%20stamped%20on%20my%20forehead%20forever%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20the%20BRICS%20as%20a%20group%20had%20achieved%20very%20little%20over%20the%20past%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20solve%20truly%20global%20issues%20without%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Europe%20-%20just%20as%20it%20was%20not%20possible%20for%20the%20West%20to%20solve%20truly%20global%20issues%20without%20China%2C%20India%20and%2C%20to%20a%20lesser%20extent%2C%20Russia%20and%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRICS%20group%20grew%20out%20of%20meetings%20between%20Russia%2C%20India%20and%20China%20which%20then%20began%20to%20meet%20more%20formally%2C%20eventually%20adding%20Brazil%2C%20then%20South%20Africa%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Iran%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20yet%20to%20formally%20join.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20now%20accounts%20for%2045%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20and%2035%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20economy%2C%20based%20on%20purchasing%20power%20parity%2C%20though%20China%20accounts%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20its%20economic%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20opened%20the%20summit%20on%20Wednesday%20by%20saying%20that%20more%20than%2030%20states%20had%20expressed%20interest%20in%20joining%20the%20group%20but%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20in%20any%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBringing%20in%20more%20members%20into%20BRICS%20would%20make%20achieving%20anything%20even%20harder%2C%20O'Neill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDollar%20challenge%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20seeking%20to%20convince%20BRICS%20countries%20to%20build%20an%20alternative%20platform%20for%20international%20payments%20that%20would%20be%20immune%20to%20Western%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Neill%2C%2067%2C%20said%20people%20had%20been%20talking%20about%20alternatives%20to%20the%20dollar%20since%20he%20started%20out%20in%20finance%20but%20that%20none%20of%20the%20countries%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20challenge%20the%20dollar%20had%20done%20anything%20to%20seriously%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20BRICS%20currency%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20be%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20China%20while%20Russia%20and%20Brazil%20would%20not%20be%20significant%20parts%20of%20it%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20really%20serious%20about%20economic%20matters%2C%20why%20don't%20they%20genuinely%20pursue%20less%20tariff%20based%20trade%20between%20each%20other%3F%26quot%3B%20O'Neill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20take%20the%20BRICS%20group%20seriously%20when%20I%20see%20signs%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20that%20really%20matter%20-%20China%20and%20India%20-%20are%20actually%20really%20trying%20to%20agree%20on%20things%2C%20rather%20than%20effectively%20trying%20to%20confront%20each%20other%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20tried%20to%20curb%20Chinese%20investments%20in%20the%20country%20since%20a%20decades%20old%20border%20dispute%20erupted%20into%20a%20clash%20between%20border%20guards%20in%202020.%20The%20two%20countries%20pledged%20to%20enhance%20cooperation%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20their%20first%20formal%20talks%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20told%20Putin%20the%20international%20situation%20was%20gripped%20by%20chaos%20but%20that%20Beijing's%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20Moscow%20was%20a%20force%20for%20stability%20amid%20the%20most%20significant%20changes%20seen%20in%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Neill%20said%20the%20G20%20had%20failed%20to%20become%20a%20sinew%20of%20truly%20global%20governance%20because%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20had%20both%20turned%20inwards%20since%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20last%20decade.%20BRICS%2C%20he%20said%2C%20lacked%20clear%20objectives%20and%20should%20take%20on%20major%20issues%20for%20humanity%20-%20such%20as%20finding%20vaccines%20or%20drugs%20against%20infectious%20diseases%2C%20or%20fighting%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729706280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Ff9ot9bng_india-china-russia_625x300_23_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrics-is-for-the-fairies-until-china-india-get-serious-says-mr-brics-6858595%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20idea%20of%20the%20BRICS%20group%20ever%20challenging%20the%20US%20dollar%20is%20for%20the%20fairies%20as%20long%20as%20China%20and%20India%20remain%20so%20divided%20and%20refuse%20to%20cooperate%20on%20trade%2C%20the%20former%20Goldman%20Sachs%20economist%20who%20came%20up%20with%20the%20BRIC%20acronym%20told%20Reuters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shiprocket%20loss%20widens%20to%20Rs%20595%20cr%20in%20FY24%20on%20restructuring%20costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729706223000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fshiprocket-loss-widens-to-rs-595-cr-in-fy24-on-restructuring-costs-124102301512_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shiprocket%20said%20that%20the%20company%20has%20reduced%20cash%20flow%20burn%20by%20almost%20half%20to%2