p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Prathiba%20M%20Singh%20orally%20said%20it%20was%20not%20inclined%20to%20declare%20Jama%20Masjid%20a%20%26quot%3Bprotected%20monument%26quot%3B%20in%20view%20of%20the%20stand%20of%20the%20ASI%20and%20ordered%20the%20petitioners%20to%20file%20their%20notes%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20steps%20that%20should%20be%20taken%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20historic%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(ASI)%20are%20saying%20there%20is%20a%20hesitation.%20There%20is%20an%20impact%20of%20declaring%20it%20a%20protected%20monument%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed%20while%20dealing%20with%20PILs%20seeking%20directions%20to%20authorities%20to%20declare%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20a%20protected%20monument%20and%20remove%20all%20encroachments%20in%20and%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20Amit%20Sharma%2C%20nonetheless%20added%20that%20it%20would%20look%20into%20the%20issue%20of%20streamlining%20the%20administration%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20asked%20the%20Delhi%20Waqf%20Board%20to%20inform%20it%20about%20the%20status%20of%20the%209-member%20managing%20committee%20that%20was%20earlier%20appointed%20for%20the%20Jama%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20is%20clear%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20not%20treated%20as%20a%20protected%20monument%2C%20its%20revenue%20cannot%20exclusively%20go%20to%20any%20private%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20while%20suggesting%20that%20some%20reimbursement%20could%20be%20given%20to%20ASI%20for%20the%20preservation%20work%20undertaken%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%2C%20represented%20by%20central%20government%20standing%20counsel%20Manish%20Mohan%2C%20stated%20in%20its%20affidavit%20that%20it%20has%20spent%20over%2060%20lakh%20on%20the%20conservation%20works%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20since%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20by%20ASI%20further%20said%20that%20since%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bprotected%20monument%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20had%20no%20information%20about%20the%20generation%20and%20utilisation%20of%20its%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20substantial%20impact%20of%20declaring%20Jama%20Masjid%20as%20a%20protected%20monument.%20The%20provision%20of%20prohibited%20area%20will%20be%20applicable%20to%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%20which%20is%20a%20100-metre%20zone%20from%20a%20protected%20monument%20in%20which%20new%20construction%20is%20prohibited.%20Further%2C%20in%20regulated%20areas%20(200%20metre%20zone%20beyond%20prohibited%20area)%20all%20construction-related%20activities%20are%20regulated%20and%20require%20prior%20permission%20from%20the%20Competent%20Authority%20and%20National%20Monuments%20Authority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%2C%20also%20represented%20by%20the%20Centre's%20standing%20counsel%20Anil%20Soni%2C%20also%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Boriginal%20file%26quot%3B%2C%20containing%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20that%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20should%20not%20be%20declared%20a%20protected%20monument%2C%20could%20not%20be%20traced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20sought%20production%20of%20the%20file%20before%20it%20on%20August%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20senior%20advocate%20DP%20Singh%2C%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%20raised%20concerns%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20utilisation%20of%20the%20revenue%20generated%20by%20the%20Jama%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20a%20world%20heritage%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20petitioner%20objected%20to%20the%20use%20of%20the%20title%20%26quot%3BShahi%20Imam%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20religious%20head%20in%20the%20Jama%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it%20was%20not%20concerned%20with%20the%20title%20but%20actual%20benefit%20to%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20happens%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20temples%20also.%20We%20are%20not%20concerned%20with%20the%20title%20but%20the%20actual%20benefit%20to%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20in%20December%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20Centre%20was%20free%20to%20place%20on%20record%20its%20views%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20streamlining%20of%20the%20revenue%20utilisation%20as%20well%20as%20the%20managing%20committee%20appointed%20by%20the%20Waqf%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20asked%20the%20ASI%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20place%20it%20a%20sketch%20along%20with%20photographs%20of%20its%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PILs%2C%20filed%20by%20Suhail%20Ahmed%20Khan%20and%20Ajay%20Gautam%20in%202014%2C%20have%20objected%20to%20the%20use%20of%20the%20title%20'Shahi%20Imam'%20by%20Jama%20Masjid's%20Imam%20Maulana%20Syed%20Ahmed%20Bukhari%20and%20the%20appointment%20of%20his%20son%20as%20the%20Naib%20(deputy)%20Imam.%20%C2%A0%20The%20pleas%20have%20also%20questioned%20why%20Jama%20Masjid%20was%20not%20under%20the%20ASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20had%20in%20August%202015%20told%20the%20court%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Singh%20had%20assured%20the%20Shahi%20Imam%20that%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20would%20not%20be%20declared%20a%20protected%20monument.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1729704060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fkklngpu8_jama-masjid_625x300_28_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdeclaring-jama-masjid-protected-monument-will-have-impact-archaeological-survey-of-india-to-court-6858251%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Archaeological%