0%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20see%20many%20of%20them%20drop%20out%20of%20school.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20him%20to%20build%20a%20hostel%20for%20children%20needing%20additional%20guidance.%20Indrakumar%20also%20runs%20a%20Sunday%20classroom%20that%20culminates%20with%20a%20campaign%20to%20safeguard%20the%20environment.%20His%20efforts%20have%20earned%20him%20a%20National%20Award%2C%20but%20the%20journey%20for%20Indrakumar%20remains%20fraught%20with%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELevelling%20the%20playing%20field%20for%20all%20students%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20shortage%20of%20staff%20to%20cater%20to%20all%20the%20needs%20of%20students%20at%20the%20primary%20school%2C%20Indrakumar%20hired%20six%20additional%20teachers%20between%201998%20and%202013.%20With%20three%20children%20to%20raise%2C%20this%20initiative%20created%20a%20significant%20financial%20burden.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20the%20additional%20strain%20raised%20concerns%20in%20the%20household%2C%20his%20son%20Khangembam%20Chinglensana%20Singh%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20a%20bakery%20had%20opened%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20My%20mother%20decided%20to%20sell%20bakery%20items%20in%20Kumbi%20and%20neighbouring%20villages%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chinglensana%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20some%20concerns%2C%20but%20we%20all%20knew%20that%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20dream%20was%20a%20righteous%20one.%20We%20continue%20to%20contribute%20in%20whatever%20way%20we%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Indrakumar%2C%20too%2C%20helps%20sell%20the%20bakery%20items%20after%20school%20hours.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20even%20sold%20a%20portion%20of%20his%20own%20land%20to%20ensure%20there%20was%20no%20fund%20shortage.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndrakumar%20was%20never%20confined%20to%20the%20classroom.%20When%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20imparting%20lessons%2C%20he%20taught%20students%20the%20importance%20of%20humility%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20and%2