chuk%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wildlife%20researcher%20from%20Ladakh%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246169%2Fladakh-snow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-saviours-rinchen-wangchuk-tsewang-namgail-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20Leopard%20Conservancy-India%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%20(SLC-IT)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20his%20successor%20(current%20director%20of%20SLC-IT)%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20understood%20very%20early%20on%20the%20need%20to%20reconcile%20snow%20leopard%20conservation%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20local%20communities%20who%20lose%20their%20livestock%2C%20particularly%20sheep%20and%20goats%2C%20to%20these%20elusive%20wild%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20growing%20up%20as%20a%20child%20herder%20in%20the%20picturesque%20Skurbuchan%20village%20in%20Leh%20district%2C%20Dr%20Namgail%20understood%20what%20it%20meant%20for%20local%20communities%20to%20lose%20their%20goats%20and%20sheep%20to%20snow%20leopards.%20This%20is%20something%20even%20the%20late%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%20and%20Jigmet%20Dadul%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20Snow%20Leopard%20naturalists%20and%20trackers%20%E2%80%94%20also%20understood%20as%20they%20spent%20entire%20winters%20living%20in%20tents%20and%20monitoring%20snow%20leopards%20in%20the%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-500x735.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Late%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-500x735.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-204x300.jpg%20204w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk-768x1129.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FRinchen-Wangchuk.jpg%20816w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-246174%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22735%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELate%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20took%20a%20variety%20of%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20needs%20of%20local%20communities%2C%20thus%20addressing%20a%20primary%20source%20of%20snow%20leopard%20deaths%20%E2%80%94%20human-animal%20conflicts.%20These%20steps%20included%20assisting%20local%20farmers%20and%20nomads%20to%20build%20structures%20that%20protect%20their%20livestock%3B%20establishing%20a%20community-controlled%20livestock%20insurance%20programme%3B%20and%20pioneering%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20models%20of%20eco-tourism%20with%20conservation-linked%20homestays%20located%20in%20critical%20snow%20leopard%20habitats.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConverting%20these%20once-angry%20locals%20into%20active%20conservationists%20is%20no%20mean%20feat.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20Jigmet%20and%20his%20son%20Nawang%20Gaylston%2C%20run%20a%20wildlife%20expedition%20company%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Snow%20Leopard%20Quest%E2%80%99%2C%20bringing%20researchers%2C%20conservationists%2C%20and%20tourists%20to%20witness%20this%20majestic%20wild%20cat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKhenrab%20Phuntsog%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F239887%2Fladakh-how-to-track-snow-leopard-rescue-wildlife-guard-khenrab-phuntsog-hemis-national-park-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhenrab%20Phuntsog%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20award-winning%20snow%20leopard%20conservationist%20with%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20experience%20as%20a%20Wildlife%20Guard%20in%20Hemis%20National%20Park%2C%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%94%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20small