betterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FIMG-20211012-WA0011.jpg%20720w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-264391%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22889%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKarma%20Sonam%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20worked%20for%20Karma%20is%20his%20natural%20ability%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20close%20relationships%20with%20different%20communities.%20Leveraging%20these%20close%20relationships%2C%20he%20convinces%20and%20incentivises%20local%20communities%20to%20work%20for%20wildlife%20conservation.%20For%20decades%2C%20pastoralists%20in%20Ladakh%20have%20had%20a%20difficult%20relationship%20with%20predators%2C%20like%20snow%20leopards%20and%20wolves%2C%20who%20prey%20on%20their%20livestock.%20Through%20his%20extensive%20grassroots%20efforts%2C%20he%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20to%20repair%20that%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoustubh%20Sharma%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Conservation%20Science%20Director%20at%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%20%E2%80%94%20has%20worked%20in%20some%20of%20the%20remotest%20and%20roughest%20terrains%20in%20the%20world%20to%20better%20understand%20snow%20leopard%20ecology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20to%20them%20by%20Dr%20Raghu%20Chundawat%2C%20a%20pioneer%20of%20snow%20leopard%20studies%20in%20India%2C%20Koustubh%20has%20dedicated%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20time%20to%20the%20Global%20Snow%20Leopard%20and%20Ecosystem%20Protection%20Programme.%20The%20programme%2C%20according%20to%20Koustubh%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbrings%20together%20governments%20from%2012%20snow%20leopard%20range%20countries%2C%20policymakers%2C%20institutions%2C%20organisations%20and%20conservationists%20toward%20securing%20the%20future%20of%20snow%20leopards%20and%20their%20mountains%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C